02:02:27,896 --> 02:02:32,313
♪ The eldest among Devas,
Lord of the Brahmanas ♪

1819
02:02:32,354 --> 02:02:36,813
♪ O Lord, we bow to you,
the protector of the sacred ♪

1820
02:02:36,813 --> 02:02:39,354
♪ Purified by a sacred bath,
clad in garments of purity ♪

1821
02:02:39,396 --> 02:02:42,854
♪ We come to you with
folded hands in prayer ♪

1822
02:02:42,854 --> 02:02:45,313
It’s tradition for those from
the forest to build the chariot.

1823
02:02:45,396 --> 02:02:47,479
- And now...?
- We’ll take over that duty from now.

1824
02:02:48,854 --> 02:02:51,854
♪ For the welfare of the world ♪

1825
02:02:51,854 --> 02:02:54,771
♪ We consecrate this statue ♪

1826
02:02:54,896 --> 02:02:59,313
♪ Uniting Shiva with
his boundless Shakti ♪

1827
02:02:59,354 --> 02:03:03,604
♪ We chant, declaring
our devotion to you ♪

1828
